  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.9.5">
<l>eppā vampalavu mivaiyēceyti ḷaittoḻintēṉ</l>
<l>tuppā niṉṉaṭiyē toṭarntēttavuṅ kiṟkiṉṟilēṉ</l>
<l>ceppārt tiṇvaraicūḻ tiruvēṅkaṭa māmalaiye</l>
<l>ṉappā vantaṭaintē ṉaṭiyēṉaiyāṭ koṇṭaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>However many sins [exist], committing these, I withered and weakened.</l>
<l>Powerful lord, I am not one who is able to even praise [you]</l>
<l rend="indent">continually at your feet.</l>
<l>My father of the great Tiruvēṅkaṭa Mountain, encircled by thick</l>
<l rend="indent">copper[-hued] peaks,</l>
<l>I came [here and] took refuge;</l>
<l rend="indent">be gracious, receiving me, your servant, in service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
